  <brief_title>Use of Dietary Supplements in Patients at Risk of Abortion Treated With Progesterone.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Supplementation With Hyaluronic Acid, Alpha-lipoic Acid, Magnesium, and Vitamin D and B6 in Patients at Risk of Abortion Treated With Progesterone: a Pilot Study.</official_title>
