  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The trial aims to investigate the effect of supplementation with hyaluronic acid,&#xD;
      alpha-lipoic acid, magnesium, vitamin D and vitamin B6 in progesterone-treated pregnant women&#xD;
      with risk factors for abortion.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
